---
title: Apricot-Mustard Chicken with Broccoli and Buttery Garlic Rice
description: This dinner turns a simple chicken recipe into a party! The rice and broccoli are perfect for picky eaters, smothered in the sweet and zippy sauce, no one can resist.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/poulet-a-la-moutarde-et-aux-abricots-ca232ff8.jpg
